* 
* 
*Smaczny, Jan (1999), &quot;Dvořák: Cello Concerto&quot;, Cambridge University Press.
*Smaczny, Jan (2002), &quot;Antonín Dvořák&quot;, in &quot;Oxford Companion to Music&quot;, ed. Alison Latham, Oxford University Press, 2002, pp. 391–92.
